Change the Layout and Style of an Input Widget

Fine-tune the input widget layout, and stylize its content for the dashboard. Input style options depend upon the selected input type.

To change the style of a slider input type:
Input widget title (1), slider input range (2), slider handle (3), slider track (4), current slider value (5).

Handle Color	Color of the position indicator on the slider track
Track Color	Color of the slider track
Show current value	Display the current slider value
Current Value Color	Color of the current slider value
Title Color	Color of the input widget title
Show values range	Display the slider range
Values Range Color	Color of the slider range

Set an input style for a freeform input type.
Input widget title (1), freeform input range (2), current freeform input value (3).

Active Value Color	Color of the freeform input value
Input Border Color	Color of the border around freeform input
Input Background Color	Background color of the freeform input
Title Color	Color of the input widget title
Values Range Color	Color of the freeform range
title: Customizing Input Widgets in Salesforce Analytics
